Name: cellular phase chronic idiopathic myelofibrosis
Definition: A vaginal adenoma that is a polyp that resembles colorectal tubulovillous adenoma.
Synonym: Cystadenoma of the extrahepatic bile duct

Name: obsolete S-T syndrome
